{"tid":1489851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【婚攝之光】藍絲攝影師為錢扮黃：點解全城㩒哂啲錢出黎仲有人like？？","createTime":"2019-08-20T03:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T02:40:53.000Z","uid":181433,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bde55334db56b6002987d94471c323169d9d2c12","tid":1489851,"uid":181433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"代朋友出post 佢實在睇唔過眼有人彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJZffPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJZffPJ.png&h=8f3f36d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Dickson Wong</span></span></strong><br />\n輕輕講下呢條友背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話說哩個攝影師之前因爲拖糧而上過新聞，係婚攝界都好出名<br />\nNow新聞link: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/technology/player?newsId=254318&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D254318%26refer%3D&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=0175f35b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D254318%26refer%3D&h=e6310a60\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/technology/player?newsId=254318&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n簡直係婚攝之光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至今都唔知找數未<br />\n於是呢位走數真漢子陰魂不散 係815襟錢日就出過篇野<br />\n聲稱襟錢既人<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">搞亂香港</span> (仲要強調自己無顏色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n當時佢聲稱<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>唔會刪post</strong></span><br />\n開口埋口就話破壞家園 但係破壞既元兇係政府又唔講？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GTjHtb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GTjHtb.png&h=7ce1b205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後引來好多人同佢理論 條友口臭到無啦啦爆佢拖糧其中既一個行家既私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(但爆完一陣又DEL 留言，咁把炮唔好del吖笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXk6ntw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXk6ntw.png&h=64874e4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最後咪又係比人屌到佢刪post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個頭鬧示威者破壞家園，既然立場咁正義，何解要刪post呀？<br />\n又要心虛，又要轉頭出嚟扮支持香港人？淆底呀？<br />\n跟住佢呢兩日又轉頭像stand with hong kong扮黃絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/111935_23e37475ffec83d0fd8c62e3904b9623.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F111935_23e37475ffec83d0fd8c62e3904b9623.png&h=91e3ba7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對佢黎講立場唔重要 所有野錢行頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家一被插 連個人個page都暫停埋 先覺得無錢搵喇 扮黃絲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知唔知你信用破哂產喇柒頭？<br />\n希望各位婚攝界/即將結婚既巴絲留意此人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />千祈唔好比生意呢條仆行做呀"},{"pid":"4b9d363cec46c2f6f29be3853d6624345a6314c3","tid":1489851,"uid":296133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"又係呢d 中立撚，見邊一邊有著數就靠邊"},{"pid":"65368c59749d04927ebedd892c2c7e011600ff2b","tid":1489851,"uid":218299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 扮嘜撚野和理非 扮嘜撚野轉立場<br />\n上次屌禁錢班人搞亂香港<br />\n仲要爆行家私隱爆得咁開心，唔繼續狙擊佢唔撚係人"},{"pid":"870c24a466d384b656a3ab28d5535649aeae7a16","tid":1489851,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"正垃圾"},{"pid":"aaec66cfb8d538bddaa302c24d1c7758118fb24f","tid":1489851,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"無顏色姐係淺藍"},{"pid":"3c0e4bcd4cd050846956cc04b1c3af88